headline.print_headline: South Korea's Mirim Lee Wins Meijer LPGA Classic
headline.main: South Korea's Mirim Lee Wins Meijer LPGA Classic

lead_paragraph: Mirim Lee won the Meijer LPGA Classic on Sunday for her first LPGA Tour victory, beating fellow South Korean player Inbee Park with a birdie on the second hole of a playoff.
